<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Order Cancellation Notification</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f4f4f4; padding: 20px;">

    <div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #fff; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);">
        <h2 style="color: #333;">Order Cancellation Notification</h2>
        <p>Dear [Customer Name],</p>
        <p>We regret to inform you that your order with the following details has been cancelled:</p>
        <p>Order ID: [Order ID]</p>
        <p>Cancelled Items:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>[Item 1]</li>
            <li>[Item 2]</li>
            <!-- Add more items if necessary -->
        </ul>
        <p>If you have already made a payment for this order, the amount will be refunded to your original payment method within [Number of Days] business days.</p>
        <p>We apologize for any inconvenience caused. If you have any questions or concerns, please feel free to contact our customer support team at [Customer Support Email].</p>
        <p>Thank you for your understanding.</p>
        <p>Sincerely,</p>
        <p>[Your Company Name]</p>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
